Wannan ya fi yadda mutane miliyan 20.4 da Nielsen ta ruwaito ranar Juma'a suka kalli wannan labarin.
Kamfanin ya ƙidaya matsakaicin masu kallo a tashoshin CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Wannan adadi ba a gano shi ba a fili ga sauran cibiyoyin sadarwa da ke nuna shi, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Kuma a gaba ɗaya, Nielsen yana da matsala wajen auna yawan masu kallo a ofishin.
