Lee, marubucin littafin "The Great Power of AI: China, Silicon Valley, and the New World Order", wanda Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, babban darektan Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya saka hannun jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin AI a kasar Sin, Face ++, ya wallafa a wannan watan.
