Jam'iyyar Labour ta Jeremy Corbyn za ta yi la'akari da wani babban shiri mai sauri wanda zai sa 'yan Birtaniya su yi aiki kwanaki hudu a mako - amma a biya su albashi na kwanaki biyar.
Jam'iyyar ta ce tana son masu gyara su ci gaba da tura tanadi da aka samu ta hanyar juyin juya halin AI ga ma'aikatan da suka yi ritaya, ta hanyar ba su karin hutu.
Yana da kyau a ga ma'aikata suna jin daɗin karshen mako na kwana uku, amma har yanzu suna iya samun albashi iri ɗaya.
Majiyoyin sun ce wannan ra'ayi na iya dacewa da tsarin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar, kuma akwai shirin sanya kasar ta zama mai karbar ma'aikata.
Majalisa ta Kungiyar Kwadago ta tallafawa sauyawa zuwa mako na kwana hudu a matsayin wata hanya ga ma'aikata masu aiki don cin gajiyar tattalin arzikin da ke canzawa.
Wani babban majiyar jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa jaridar The Sunday Times cewa ana sa ran sanar da sake duba manufofin kafin karshen shekara.
Ba zai faru ba da dare, amma mako guda na kwanaki hudu shine burin da ake so, wanda ya dace da hanyar jam'iyyar don daidaita tattalin arzikin, tare da ba da izinin ma'aikata, da kuma tsarin masana'antu na jam'iyyar.
Jam'iyyar Labour ba ita ce ta farko da ta goyi bayan wannan ra'ayi ba, har ma da Green Party, wanda ya yi alkawarin yin aiki kwana hudu a mako a lokacin yakin neman zaben shekarar 2017.
Wannan burin a halin yanzu ba shi da goyon baya daga dukkan 'yan jam'iyyar Labour.
Duk da haka, mai magana da yawun jam'iyyar Labour ya ce: "Ba manufofin jam'iyyar bane a yi aiki kwana hudu a mako, kuma jam'iyyar bata yi la'akari da wannan burin ba".
