Menene bikin Global Citizen Festival kuma shin ya yi wani abu don rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar, New York City za ta karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen Festival, wani biki na shekara-shekara wanda ke nuna manyan fitattun mutane masu ban sha'awa da kuma ayyuka masu ban sha'awa da kuma manufa ta gama gari don kawo karshen talauci a duniya.
Yanzu da yake cikin shekara ta bakwai, bikin na 'yan ƙasa na duniya zai ga dubun dubatar mutane suna zuwa babban filin shakatawa na Central Park don ba kawai jin daɗin wasan kwaikwayon Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma don haɓaka ingantaccen burin taron don kawo ƙarshen talauci ta hanyar 2030.
Bikin na Global Citizens, wanda aka fara a 2012, wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya ta duniya da ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan masu fafutuka.
Don samun tikiti kyauta don halartar taron (sai dai idan kuna son biyan kuɗin VIP), masu halartar wasan kwaikwayon dole ne su cika wasu ayyuka ko ayyuka na yau da kullun, kamar yin aikin sa kai, aika imel ga shugabannin duniya, yin kiran waya, ko wasu hanyoyi masu ma'ana don taimakawa ci gaban burin su na kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya nasarar da Global Citizen ya samu tare da shekaru 12 da suka rage don cimma burinsa?
