Girgizar kasa da tsunami a Indonesia
A kalla mutane 384 aka kashe a girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, kuma adadin zai karu, a cewar jami'an.
Saboda katsewar sadarwa, jami'an ceto ba su iya samun wani bayani daga yankin Donggala da ke arewacin Palu ba, wanda ke kusa da girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane sama da 16,000 bayan bala'in ya auku.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Central Sulawesi ne, wanda ke a ƙarshen wani ɗan ƙaramin ƙaton bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da kusan mazaunan 379,800 a 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa lokacin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka afkawa.
Donggala ƙasa ce mai ƙarfi da ke da nisan kilomita 300 a gabar tekun tsibirin Sulawesi.
Ƙasar da ke ƙarƙashin wannan iko, yanki ne na yanki wanda ke da yawan jama'a 299,200 a 2017.
Kifi da noma sune tushen tattalin arzikin tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala.
Har ila yau, hakar ma'adinai na da mahimmanci a wannan lardin, amma mafi yawan suna tattare a Morowali a gabar tekun Sulawesi.
A cewar hukumar kula da bala'i ta Indonesia, tsibirin Palu da Donggala sun sha wahala daga tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane sama da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Wani tsunami kuma ya afkawa Donggala ta yamma a shekarar 1996, inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana kan wutar girgizar kasa ta Pacific kuma ana yawan samun girgizar kasa.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar kasa da tsunamis a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Wata babbar girgizar kasa a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin tsibirin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta haifar da guguwar tsunami da ta addabi kasashe 14, ta kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin wadanda suka mutu a lardin Aceh.
2005: Wata girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa gabar yammacin Sumatra a karshen watan Maris da farkon watan Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias a gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afku a kudu maso gabashin tsibirin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afku a gabar kudu, inda ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afku a kusa da Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane sama da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai a Sumatra, ta haifar da guguwar tsunami mai tsawon mita 10, ta lalata kauyuka da dama kuma ta kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya a lardin Aceh, inda ta haddasa barna da fargaba yayin da ake tunatar da mazauna yankin game da bala'in da girgizar kasa da tsunami ta haifar a 2004.
Babu wata guguwar tsunami da ta fashe a yanzu, amma sama da mutane 100 sun mutu sakamakon rushewar ginin.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin yawon bude ido na Lombok na Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon bude ido suka makale.
