A cewar wani rahoto da 'yan sanda na jihar Alaska suka fitar a ranar Asabar, an kama Palin, mai shekara 29, a Wasaga, Alaska, bisa zargin cin zarafin mata da maza da kuma hana kama shi.
A cewar rahoton 'yan sanda, lokacin da wata mace da ta sani ta yi ƙoƙarin kiran' yan sanda don bayar da rahoton laifin da aka zarge ta, sai ya karɓi wayar daga gare ta.
