Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya suna neman hukuncin kisa mai wuya ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York City wanda ya kashe mutane takwas, wanda shine hukuncin kisa wanda ba a taba yankewa a jihar ba don aikata laifukan tarayya tun 1953.
An zargi Saipov, mai shekaru 30, da yin amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don yin fashin keke a kan hanyar West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, wanda ya buge masu tafiya da masu hawa a kan hanyarsa a watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da cancantar hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su nuna cewa Saipov ya "kisa" kashe mutane takwas da kuma haifar da mummunan rauni "da gangan", a cewar sanarwar niyyar neman hukuncin kisa da aka shigar a Kudancin Yankin New York.
A cewar takardun kotun, hukuncin kisa ne kawai za a yanke wa masu laifin.
Makonni bayan harin, wani alkalin kotun tarayya ya yanke wa Saipov hukuncin kisa a kan laifuka 22, ciki har da laifuka takwas na kisan kai, a cikin wani laifi na cinikin wayoyin hannu, wanda hukumomin tarayya ke amfani da su a cikin aikata laifuka da ake yi da kuma zargin tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci "babban shiri da taka tsantsan", suna mai bayyana yadda Saipov ya aiwatar da shi a matsayin "ta'addanci, zalunci da rashin hankali".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa danginsa da abokansa rauni da lalacewaDiego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", in ji bayanin da aka yi game da niyyar.
Wadanda suka mutu biyar daga cikin su 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma kenan da yanke hukuncin kisa a gundumar kudancin New York.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa na kisan dillalan miyagun kwayoyi biyu, amma an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A kwanan nan, an yanke hukuncin kisa a cikin wani shari'ar tarayya a New York a 1953 ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata, kuma an kashe su bayan an yanke musu hukunci kan yin ta'addanci ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe Rosenbergs biyu ta wurin kujera na lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
