Rahoton da aka bayar kwanan nan daga Hukumar Kifi da Daji ta Florida ya nuna cewa an samu raguwar yawan masu ruwa da tsaki a wasu yankunan yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, an bayar da rahoton yaduwar cutar a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier Counties - wanda ke nuna raguwar taron.
Wannan yaduwar ruwan teku ta narke ta kusan mil 130 daga bakin tekun Pinellas ta arewa zuwa kudu maso kudancin Lee County.
An gano ragowar kusan mil 10 daga gabar tekun Hillsborough County, amma a cikin ƙananan yankuna fiye da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma lura da ambaliyar ruwa a cikin lardin Pasco.
